{"tid":504741,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香港人就係永不滿足］中環摩天輪重開$20！市民：可惜小童冇半價","createTime":"2017-12-20T11:00:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-20T12:57:16.000Z","uid":22675,"like":2,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"f9653d71b848d0350bfec31afacd1002070ed229","tid":504741,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T11:00:09.000Z","msg":"中環海濱摩天輪今日重開，11時正式開幕前已有逾百市民在場排隊等候乘搭。乘搭的市民大讚減價後票價合適，會考慮與親友再次乘搭。主辦方則指網上購票銷情熱烈，已加開少量平安夜、聖誕節門票。<br />\n<br />\n中環海濱摩天輪早前涉及易手風波，於今日重開，票價由100元大幅減至20元，另設長者半價優惠，而重開「頭班車」於早上11時開出。工作人員指摩天輪每程3圈，共約15分鐘；記者實測則每程連同停留時間共約20分鐘。<br />\n<br />\n李生李太帶同兩名孫女乘搭「頭班車」，早上10時半已經到場。李生稱以往因票價太貴而少有乘搭，今次雖為沒有小童半價優惠而感到可惜，但仍大讚值回票價，「（以前）4個人400蚊，而家80蚊我仲有320蚊去食飯」。李生又指摩天輪車廂舒適，會考慮再預約除夕夜晚再次乘搭。<br />\n<br />\n劉太亦帶同孫兒乘搭摩天輪，得知重開及減價而特意前來，認為20元是合適票價。劉太讚摩天輪車廂「好定、好舒服」，風景亦好，「大會堂好似火柴盒咁」，指會再與家人朋友包廂觀賞夜景。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171220/57604911\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171220%2F57604911&d=Xd07no4XomrZPhsnyzK6av9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=52a16041\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20171220%2F57604911&h=26a9c40a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20171220/57604911</a>"},{"pid":"b65acdceed8fb45000dda3dddc581b6e3bbb44a5","tid":504741,"uid":161732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T11:14:50.000Z","msg":"人心不足蛇吞象"},{"pid":"e74507f9be67892c03ea1ac017d195c1160ae1b1","tid":504741,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T11:16:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人心不足蛇吞象</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07645febfb338144315b608efbd39231954ddacd","tid":504741,"uid":43470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T11:20:26.000Z","msg":"同香港人講骨氣真係曬撚氣"},{"pid":"3e3ebe9789844574c15e44be72ba2f22ee881675","tid":504741,"uid":5499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T11:27:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同香港人講骨氣真係曬撚氣</blockquote><br />\n第二日就咩都唔記得啦"},{"pid":"8975e6418648cbd151e6888bc7dcffb785978bae","tid":504741,"uid":96,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T11:29:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同香港人講骨氣真係曬撚氣</blockquote><br />\n第二日就咩都唔記得啦</blockquote><br />\n有冇諗過呢班人本來就唔睇新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbdb12aaae3f1e834748426f29af01a100d90efc","tid":504741,"uid":29295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T11:29:28.000Z","msg":"長者半價<br />\n比啲廢老坐到冧埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ae8c30d56a23e9d8c95a0f6e17bfac14e4af918","tid":504741,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T12:48:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca77cdce306e2e1ba198cb41a2c04b746e340475","tid":504741,"uid":1067,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T12:51:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>長者半價<br />\n比啲廢老坐到冧埋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩蚊乘坐摩天輪優惠"},{"pid":"26f27f4484f2ca1120b0e5a4a086a9d379db9a95","tid":504741,"uid":42188,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T12:52:45.000Z","msg":"咁直接將成人票價加到$40<br />\n小童就有半價$20<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0cba1fc65e18b8d6486c84b1e59780e73d018ab7","tid":504741,"uid":155568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T12:53:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"5e09fe98f77cb6788ea1170dfc6d7855dfc563ed","tid":504741,"uid":16613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy